{"tid":1902540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉販毒青年被捕後不適　警押往明愛醫院求診時逃脫","createTime":"2020-02-28T11:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:12:18.000Z","uid":212626,"like":364,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"662f1463cf7b2f878623d779e193bd39d2812bcc","tid":1902540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"一名涉嫌販毒被捕的男子於扣查期間報稱不適，今早（28日）約8時30分，由警方帶往深水埗明愛醫院求診時逃脫，有警員到場增援，在附近一帶搜查及兜截，暫未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n逃脫的18歲男子姓譚，身高約1.75米，中等身材，黃皮膚，事發時身穿黑色上衣及黑色短褲，警方呼籲市民如有任何資料提供，請致電3661 9782與調查人員聯絡，或致電999報案。案件暫列從合法羈押逃脫處理，由深水埗警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，旺角警區特別職務隊探員根據線報，昨晚（27日）7時許，於石硤尾邨美映樓停車場截查譚姓男子，在其身上檢獲約1.8公斤懷疑氯胺酮（K仔），市值約110萬元，他涉嫌販毒被捕，其後由探員帶返警署扣留調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200228/s00001/1582884624620/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200228%2Fs00001%2F1582884624620%2F&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=bd0a4f8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200228%2Fs00001%2F1582884624620%2F&h=f2ba4574\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200228/s00001/1582884624620/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a454a0777b863e78bd1aafd20e50e10e452e24a","tid":1902540,"uid":50386,"like":621,"dislike":3,"score":618,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"捉文宣就重兵捉<br />\n捉販毒就放軟手腳<br />\n仲話要加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb5513c5e9f64d3d3b7ec2b74de19f381203599","tid":1902540,"uid":71748,"like":128,"dislike":3,"score":125,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"1.8公斤咁平？"},{"pid":"2ee1a7e9aeefdc9ea51931598a835af35e20f0a1","tid":1902540,"uid":101968,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T